summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 228W page 19, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1 & 2, less east 148' thereof, Block 6, University Lake Shore Add., Div. No. 1, located on the southeast corner of 35th Ave. N.E. and E. 125th St., from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone, to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
